f=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qdt1665703032118.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdt1665703032118.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdt1665703032118.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qdt1665703032118\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Glyph\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__glyph_315801\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Glyph defines is an image in a Uniface-proprietary format that is OS-independent and DBMS-independent.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96152e1_d96153e1_d96154e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nbf1705582294349.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbf1705582294349.html\" title=\"Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats.\">Glyphs</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__topic_d64247e1_d64248e1_d64249e1_d64250e1_d64251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d524108e63\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">gly</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphyName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Size</var>.gly</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665703032118__table_d10673e1_d10674e1_d10675e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName.Language</var>:gly:<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__topic_d64252e1_d64253e1_d64254e1_d64255e1_d64256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d524108e265\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96161e1_d96162e1_d96163e1\">Glyph specializes Development Object in the following\n            ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38936e1_d38937e1_d38938e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96164e1_d96165e1_d96166e1\">It has an untyped library as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38939e1_d38940e1_d38941e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96167e1_d96168e1_d96169e1\">It has properties, but no code containers or\n                  other development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__topic_d64257e1_d64258e1_d64259e1_d64260e1_d64261e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d524108e289\"> Properties </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38942e1_d38943e1_d38944e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38945e1_d38946e1_d38947e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cfv1665702708639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cfv1665702708639.html\" title=\"Language code for the global object with which you are working.\">Language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38948e1_d38949e1_d38950e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96173e1_d96174e1_d96175e1\">The following properties are derived from the original\n            image and cannot be changed.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38951e1_d38952e1_d38953e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Height</span>—height of the glyph in pixels; read-only. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38954e1_d38955e1_d38956e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Width</span>—width of the glyph in pixels; read-only.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__li_d38957e1_d38958e1_d38959e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Colors</span>—number of colors\n               used in the image; read-only. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665703032118__p_d96176e1_d96177e1_d96178e1\">Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so\n            the properties <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI-Specific</span>, and\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Full-Color</span> cannot be modified.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615374\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615374\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Glyph Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Glyph A Glyph defines is an image in a Uniface-proprietary format that is OS-independent and DBMS-independent. For more information, see Glyphs . Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: gly Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: GlyphyName @ Library @ Language @ Size .gly URI format: lib: LibraryName.Language :gly: GlyphName Specialization Glyph specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has an untyped library as parent. It has properties, but no code containers or other development objects. Properties Name Language Description The following properties are derived from the original image and cannot be changed. Height —height of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Width —width of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Colors —number of colors used in the image; read-only. Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so the properties GUI , GUI-Specific , and Full-Color cannot be modified. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}